						<p><hi rend="bold">Māṟavarmaṉ Tribhº (Kings name lost): Year 27.</hi></p>						

						<p>This inscription is too fragmentary.</p>						

						<p>It mentions Āda[ṉūr] in Śūraṅguḍi-nāḍu and Muduguḍi-nāḍu and some people like Pavittiramāṇi[kkam] Gaṅgadēvaṉ. It appears to record a gift of a <hi rend="italic">nandā</hi> lamp.</p>						

